_tp_x= \mathbb{P}\left( T\left( x\right) >t\right) =1- {_tq_x}=1-\mathbb{P}\left( T\left( x\right) \leq t\right).
\end{eqnarray*}
}
{{Indeed}}, the probability, for a live $\left( x \right) $, to remain alive $t$ more years is given by
\begin{eqnarray*}
_tp_x=\mathbb{P}\left( X > x+t\mid X>x\right)=\frac{\mathbb{P}\left( X>x+t\right)}{\mathbb{P}\left( X>x\right)}=\frac{S\left( x+t \right)}{S\left( x\right) }.
\end{eqnarray*}

